overview:
Established in the year 1989, We, “Sd Powertech”, are prominent name, which is engaged in manufacturing and trading a wide range of Smart Socket, CFL Inverter & Power Saver. These Smart Sockets, CFL Inverter & Power Saver are manufactured using premium grade raw material, sourced from dependable vendors of the market.

Our Team; Skilled workers Sales and marketing personnel Production engineers Testing engineers Research and development expert

Our Infrastructure: We have constructed a state-of-the-art infrastructure, which helps us immensely in controlling the business related activities smoothly and systematically. Along with this, the facility is equipped with all the essential amenities that are needed for offering an unparalleled range of Smart Socket, AC Power Saver and CFL Inverter.

Quality Assurance: Quality remains an impeccable strength, which aids us immensely in rising our stature in this stiff market competition. Hence, we have constructed a sophisticated quality checking laboratory, which is installed with modern machines and innovative technology that aid us in offering a defect-free range of Smart Socket, AC Power Saver and CFL Inverter.

Client Satisfaction: We are able to attain maximum satisfaction of our respectable customers, by offering an extensive range of Smart Socket, AC Power Saver and CFL Inverter. These products are developed using optimum grade raw material, sourced from trusted vendors of the market. Moreover, our professionals keep a constant communication with the clients, in order to know and understand their exact requirements effectively.
